An official letter from Caijing magazine.
《财经》杂志由中国证券市场研究中心主办，1998年创刊，秉承“独立、独家、独到”的新闻理念，以权威性、公正性、专业性报道见长，是政经学界决策者、研究者、管理者的必读刊物。
"Caijing" magazine, sponsored by the China Securities Market Research Center, was founded in 1998, upholding the news concept of "independence, exclusivity and originality," and providing authoritative, impartial and professional reports.
。
.
美国确诊和死亡病例都在快速上升，本周内将进行100万份检测，预计还会有较大增长文 |《财经》数据研究员徐进 图 |《财经》视觉中心 编辑 | 郝洲一、武汉拉锯进入扫尾阶段，境外输入性病例构成新风险图1今日国内简述：国内3月2日报告累计病例80151例，新增125例，低于韩国、意大利、伊朗等国。
The number of confirmed and fatal cases in the U.S. is rising rapidly, with a million tests due this week, and is expected to grow at a much larger pace. Caijing Data Researcher Xu Jin-tou and Wuhan La Jing entered the final stage.
新增病例111例来自武汉，广大非武汉地区14例，其中已确定7例属境外（意大利）输入病例。
Of the 111 new cases from Wuhan and 14 cases from non-Wuhan areas, 7 cases were confirmed as imported from abroad.
辽宁丹东3例亦可能为境外输入病例。
Three cases of Dandong Liaoning may also be imported from abroad.
北京再回零新增。
Beijing adds nothing to the list.
武汉基本确认已经走出持续12天的“中位拉锯平台”（图1，武汉新增确诊、病死、治愈人数），即将转入扫尾阶段，不过，中央明确指示，各项防控工作仍然不能放松。
Wuhan has basically confirmed that it has stepped out of the 12-day "median pull-saw platform" (Figure 1, number of newly diagnosed, sickened and cured in Wuhan) and is about to enter its final phase, although the central government has given clear instructions that control efforts should not be relaxed.
由于武汉救治能力的提升，使得全国总治愈率持续以较快速度增升，在刚刚夸过50%这一节点之后，将于本周内陆续跨过60、70、80%关口。
As a result of the improvement in Wuhan's treatment capacity, the overall cure rate continues to rise at a faster rate across the country, passing the threshold of 60, 70 and 80 per cent by the end of this week.
另一方面，复工复产正在湖北以外各省市有序加快展开，上证指数已从疫情悲观时的2685点重回3000一线（3月3日报收2994.53点），创业版更创一年来新高。
On the other hand, the resumption of work is proceeding at an orderly and accelerated pace in provinces and cities outside Hubei Province. The Shanghai index has returned to the 3,000-point mark (2,994.53 points in the 3 March daily) from 2685 during the pessimism of the epidemic, and the start-up version has reached a year-long high.
二、海外确诊数字过万，病毒已蔓延至72国（不含中国）图2海外的确诊病例持续以每日超过千例的速度在增加，已突破10000大关。
The number of confirmed overseas cases has spread to 72 countries (excluding China). The number of confirmed cases overseas continues to increase at a rate of over 1000 per day, surpassing the 10000 mark.
美国确诊病例将近100，死亡病例增加至6例。
In the United States, nearly 100 cases were confirmed and the number of deaths increased to 6.
德国、法国、西班牙三国病例增长的势头仍然得不到有效遏制。
The increase in the number of cases in Germany, France, and Spain remains largely unchecked.
图3在中国以外，疫情扩散主要集中在西太平洋（韩国）、欧洲（意大利、德国、法国和西班牙）和东地中海地区（伊朗），以上地区的确诊总数占海外总确诊人数的90%以上。
Figure 3 Outside China, the spread of the epidemic is concentrated in the Western Pacific (Republic of Korea), Europe (Italy, Germany, France and Spain) and the Eastern Mediterranean (Iran), which together account for more than 90 per cent of the total number of confirmed cases overseas.
图4国内疫情的进一步趋缓，韩国、意大利和伊朗这三个国家的单日新增已经远远超过中国。
Figure 4 shows a further slowing of the epidemic, with three countries - South Korea, Italy, and Iran - adding far more each day than China.
世卫组织总干事谭德塞表示，中国以外地区的单日新增病例已经是中国境内的9倍之多。
Outside China, the number of new cases a day is already nine times higher than in China, said WHO Director-General Edwards.
三、韩国进入“作战”状态图5图6韩国“新天地”教会成员（总数约为21.5万）仍在陆续接受病毒检测。
Photo 6 Members of the New World Church in South Korea (a total of about 215,000) are still being tested for the virus.
新增病例依然居高不下。
New cases remain high.
新增病例主要集中在大邱市，占韩国新增总数的86.50%，确诊总数占韩国国内病例总数的74.81%。
The majority of new cases were in Daegu, accounting for 86.50 per cent of the total number of new cases in Korea and 74.81 per cent of the total number of cases in the country.
韩国总统文在寅已经宣布韩国所有政府机构进入24小时紧急“作战”状态。
South Korean President Win Yin has declared a 24-hour emergency "war" status for all government agencies in South Korea.
四、欧洲疫情呈燎原之势图7欧盟的“核心区”如今也成为了新冠肺炎疫情扩散的核心区，但主要新增数字仍然由意大利贡献。
The European Union's "heart zone" is now at the heart of the spread of the outbreak of pneumonia in Europe, but Italy is still to blame for much of the increase.
北欧的挪威和西北欧的尼德兰增长有所抬头。
Growth picked up in northern Europe in Norway and in Nedland in north-west Europe.
【特别说明：以上统计，2月28日前为世卫组织官方统计数据，数据截止时间为北京时间每日17时；从2月28日开始，数据由《财经》根据公开资料统计，截止时间为北京时间每日9时】五、全球疫情数字速览1、【10万人检测试剂】一架装载了世卫组织援助物资的飞机3月2日抵达伊朗，世卫组织代表也同机抵达，以评估目前伊朗新冠肺炎疫情状况。
2007-9-24 16: 19 [hide] Statistics above indicate that February 28 is the official WHO statistics, the cut-off time is 17: 00 daily Beijing time; from Feb. 28, the deadline is 9: 00 p.m. Beijing time.
此架飞机上装有7.5吨医疗用品和设备，可供15000人使用。
The aircraft contained 7.5 tons of medical supplies and equipment for 15,000 people.
其中还包括一批新冠病毒检测试剂，可供10万人使用。
It also includes a batch of new crown virus detection reagents, which can be used by 100,000 people.
目前世卫组织驻伊朗办事处也有一名员工确诊，症状轻微。
An employee of the WHO office in Iran has also been diagnosed with mild symptoms.
2、【30万亿韩元】韩国总统文在寅下令韩国政府所有机构进入“24小时紧急戒备系统”，需加强检疫措施戒，并准备推进相关经济措施。
2007-9-24 16: 29 [hide] South Korean President Wen Jin Yin ordered all South Korean government agencies to enter the 24-hour emergency alert system, strengthen quarantine measures and prepare for economic measures.
文在寅认为韩国当前“经济形势严峻，”韩国政府将斥资30万亿韩元（约合人民币1751亿元）以处理新冠肺炎危机，包括计划的补充预算。
Wen said South Korea's current "economic situation is grim." The South Korean government will spend 30 trillion won (175.1 billion yuan) to deal with the Crowne Pneumonia crisis, including a planned supplementary budget.
3、【100万检测计划】美国疾病控制与预防中心存在缺陷的诊断方法遭到诟病，试剂存在的缺陷导致检测结果并不可靠。
[center for disease control and prevention] The U.S. Centers for Disease Control and Prevention has been criticized for faulty diagnosis, and defects in reagents have led to unreliable testing results.
负责抗疫的美国副总统彭斯特别工作组宣布，本周内将进行100万次的检测。
Vice President Burns, who oversees the fight against the disease, announced one million tests this week.
为扩大检测范围，美国一些私营公司和研究机构已经获得检测授权，美国的确诊病例很可能会出现激增。
A number of private companies and research institutes in the United States have been granted testing authorizations to expand testing, and there is a high risk of a spike in confirmed cases in the United States.
小结：不到一周前，海外新增病例的数字刚刚超过中国，与中国“齐头并进”，但是如今已是中国的9倍之多。
Wrap-up: Less than a week ago, the number of new cases overseas just surpassed that of China, "keeping pace" but now nine times that of China.
在中国有序展开复工复产之际，海外输入性病例成为中国的防疫新风险。
As China resumes production in an orderly manner, imported cases from overseas have become a new risk for China's epidemic prevention.
